SpecKit Workflow:

- `/specify [feature]` → create spec in `specs/{id}-{name}/`
- `/index` → verify and fix spec/fix indexation (conflicts, gaps)
- Review `spec.md`, `plan.md`, `tasks.md`
- `/implement {id}` → execute tasks following TDD
- `/review-implement` → code review
- Track progress in `tasks.md` and `_todo.md`

Spec Structure:

- `specs/{id}-{name}/spec.md` — detailed specification
- `specs/{id}-{name}/plan.md` — implementation plan
- `specs/{id}-{name}/tasks.md` — task breakdown with checkboxes
- `specs/{id}-{name}/research.md` — optional research notes

Indexation:

- **See rule `5-spec-indexing.mdc`** for complete indexation rules
- Index format: 3-digit zero-padded (`001`, `002`, ..., `999`)
- Shared index space: `specs/` + `fixes/` + `specs/archive/`
- Sequence must be continuous with increment of 1 — no gaps, no duplicates
- Use `/index` to detect and resolve conflicts after branch merges

Roadmap (from ROADMAP_AGENTS_IA.md):

- Phase 0: Bootstrap & DX (`specs/001-bootstrap-dx/`)
- Phase 1: auth-api + App Registry (`specs/002-auth-bff/`, `specs/003-app-registry/`)
- Phase 2: Entitlements + Hub Shell (`specs/004-entitlements/`, `specs/005-hub-shell/`)
- Phase 3: App Starter + Integration Kits (`specs/006-app-starter/`)
- Phase 4: Feature Flags + Hub AI Module (`specs/007-feature-flags/`, `specs/008-hub-ai-module/`)
- Phase 5: Event Bus + Documentation Hub (`specs/009-event-bus/`, `specs/010-documentation-hub/`)
- Platform: Local Dev DNS/TLS (`specs/011-local-dev-platform/`)

Rules:

- Always read the relevant spec before implementing
- Update tasks.md as you complete work
- Follow TDD — write failing test first
- Before creating a new spec/fix, apply indexation rules from `5-spec-indexing.mdc`
